332.302.  Definitions. — As used in sections 332.302 to 332.305, the following terms shall mean: 
  (1)  "Committee", the dental hygienist distance learning committee created under section 332.303; 
  (2)  "Department", the department of economic development; 
  (3)  "Director", the director of the department of economic development.
(L. 2005 S.B. 177)
